ads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/taylor-swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>谈到了毁灭性的洛杉矶野火——看看她下面是怎么说的。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259">洛杉矶音乐界告诉我们野火的“悲剧性”影响：“这种影响将持续多年”</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周（1 月 7 日），洛杉矶<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">遭遇多场单独的野火</a>，摧毁了多个社区，并迫使超过 15 万居民撤离。大火已导致数千所房屋被烧毁，已造成<a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/live-updates/la-fires-southern-california-containment-efforts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">27 人死亡</a>、 <a href="https://www.latimes.com/california/story/2025-01-16/how-many-people-are-missing-from-the-los-angeles-fires" target="_blank" rel="noopener">31 人失踪</a>。</p><p>现在，斯威夫特<a href="https://www.instagram.com/stories/taylorswift/?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在 Instagram Stories 上评论了加州的灾难</a>。她写道：“加利福尼亚州的大火摧毁了许多家庭，看到这些故事的发生令人心碎。如此多的痛苦、损失和破坏。当许多人开始经历人生中最具挑战性的时期时，也有许多令人惊叹的组织和团体联合起来帮助这些社区重建。” </p><figure id="attachment_3823675" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3823675" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3823675" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Taylor-Swift.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_TAS24_Getty-Images-for-TAS-Rights-Management-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3823675" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒·斯威夫特。图片来源：Kevin Winter/TAS24/Getty Images for TAS Rights Management</figcaption></figure><p>她继续说道，她已经向多个组织捐款，并敦促追随者如果有能力也这样做：“这些是我捐赠过的组织。如果您觉得有必要或有能力捐款，请这样做。”</p><p>她重点介绍的组织和资源包括 211 LA、加州社区基金会、大洛杉矶仁人家园、洛杉矶消防局基金会、洛杉矶联合学区教育基金会和 MusiCares。</p><p>她捐款的组织之一直接救济组织感谢泰勒·斯威夫特“在支持受破坏性野火影响的人们方面表现出令人难以置信的慷慨和同情心”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">感谢您<a href="https://twitter.com/taylorswift13?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@taylorswift13</a> ，感谢您为支持南加州毁灭性野火影响的人们提供的令人难以置信的慷慨和同情心。 <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1faf6.png" alt="🫶" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/lafires?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#lafires</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Californiafires?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Californiafires</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/eaton?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#eaton</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/altadena?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#altadena</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/losangeles?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#losangeles</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/fires?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#fires</a> <a href="https://t.co/BKkGYUK3hY">pic.twitter.com/BKkGYUK3hY</a></p><p> - 直接救援 (@DirectRelief) <a href="https://twitter.com/DirectRelief/status/18800244027